Process called "list_secrets_from_backend" that takes filters as Dictionary[String, Any] and pagination as Dictionary[String, Any] and store as SecretStore returns Dictionary[String, Any]:
    Note: List secrets from backend with filtering and pagination
    Return dictionary containing "success" as true, "secrets" as list containing, "error_message" as ""

Process called "get_secret_metadata_from_backend" that takes secret_id as String and store as SecretStore returns Dictionary[String, Any]:
