    Return data

Process called "notify_secret_rotation" that takes secret_id as String and old_version as Integer and new_version as Integer and config as Dictionary[String, Any] returns None:
    Note: Notify systems of secret rotation
    Return None

Process called "schedule_next_rotation" that takes secret_id as String and interval as Float and store as SecretStore returns None:
    Note: Schedule next automatic rotation
    Return None
:End Note